## Features
### User Authentication
- Secure signup and login system
- Password hashing with bcrypt
- Session-based authentication
- Authorization checks for protected routes

### Event Management
- Create, Read, Update, Delete (CRUD) operations
- Event categorization (professional/social)
- Host information tracking
- Date and time management
- Image support for events

### Security Features
- Input validation
- Authorization checks
- Protected routes
- Secure password storage
- Session management

### User Experience
- Flash messages for feedback
- Dynamic navigation based on user status
- Responsive design
- Error handling with user-friendly messages

## MVC Structure
### Models
- User: Authentication and user data
- Event: Event management with host reference

### Views
- User views: signup, login, profile
- Event views: index, show, create, edit
- Partial views: header, footer
- Error handling views

### Controllers
- User controller: Authentication logic
- Event controller: Event management logic
- Error handling middleware

